{"type": "article", "id": 5416, "title": "智能配奶机 Milking", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-21T07:27:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233849f9rkmxuOwnP3jhbL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自北京的创业团队婴萌科技带来了他们的首款产品智能配奶机 Milking。这是一款针对于新手爸妈的利器，想要解决给婴儿喂奶占用时间太多的问题。 Milking 另配有一款相应的手机应用，需要给小孩喂奶粉时，只需扫描奶粉包装的二维码，通过玻璃面板进行一键配奶操作，这款智能配奶机酒可以自动进行奶粉配比，奶量、浓度都可以进行精确控制，还能减少每次冲泡奶粉的时间。目前， Milking 已经在<a href=\"http://hi.taobao.com/market/hi/detail2014.php?spm=a215p.1260087.0.0.A9C3DV&amp;id=4528#report\" target=\"_blank\">淘宝众筹平台</a>达成众筹目标，售价 499 元起，预计本月底出货。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODIwNDU0NzA0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233847wS8dD76A4kt52MrJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7234375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233848rUTKJ4n0aDsZGXcw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233848sgC12oD4Wh0UeB3A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}